# Workflow

Read [.notebook/README.md](../../.notebook/README.md) and [.workflow-sldc/01_WORKFLOW.md](../../.workflow-sldc/01_WORKFLOW.md) before plan, design, or backlog work.

## Folder order

`00_references` → `01` → `02` → `03` → `04_wbs` → `.backlogs/{id}/` (draft → ready → design) → `06_design` → code → `05_reports`

Do not store raw intake in the repo.

## Skill routing

Invoke matching skills from `.cursor/skills/`:

### Define

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Intent unclear (who/why/success) | `interview-me` |
| Many options / MVP | `idea-refine` |
| Raw intake → one draft task | `create-task-draft` |
| Catalog / scope impact (01–03) | `spec-driven-development` |

### Plan

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Split tasks, INVEST, status `ready` | `planning-and-task-breakdown` |

### Design

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Task `ready`, before develop (M+ bắt buộc) | `design-workflow` |

### TDD · Develop

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Test fail (RED) after design | `test-driven-development` |
| Implement slice by slice (GREEN) | `incremental-implementation` |
| UI / accessibility | `frontend-ui-engineering` |
| API / contract design | `api-and-interface-design` |
| Better agent context | `context-engineering` |
| Doc-verified framework code | `source-driven-development` |
| High-stakes / unfamiliar code | `doubt-driven-development` |

### Verify · Test

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Browser runtime verification | `browser-testing-with-devtools` |
| Test fail, build break, unexpected behavior | `debugging-and-error-recovery` |

### Review

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Pre-merge review | `code-review-and-quality` |
| Code works but too complex | `code-simplification` |
| Auth, input, secrets, deps | `security-and-hardening` |
| Perf requirements or regression | `performance-optimization` |

### Ship · Deploy

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Commits, branches, PR hygiene | `git-workflow-and-versioning` |
| CI/CD pipelines | `ci-cd-and-automation` |
| Sunset / migration | `deprecation-and-migration` |
| ADRs, API docs | `documentation-and-adrs` |
| Logs, metrics, traces | `observability-and-instrumentation` |
| Pre-launch, rollout, rollback | `shipping-and-launch` |

### Report

| Situation | Skill |
|-----------|-------|
| Task `done` → PM/client handover | `report-writer` |

Checklists: [.notebook/00_references/](../../.notebook/00_references/README.md)

## Pipeline

```
INTAKE → define → plan → ready → design → tdd → develop → review → test → deploy → report
```

Do not set task status `ready` without INVEST and human approval.  
Do not implement M+ work without `.backlogs/{id}/design/{id}.md`.

